z=i\frac{1}{r}
\operatorname{Res}(f(z),z=\frac{i}{r^{n}})=\large\lim_{z\to i\frac{1}{r^{n}}}(z-i\frac{1}{r^{n}})f(z)=\large\lim_{z\to i\frac{1}{r^{n}}}\frac{1}{r^n}(r^nz-i)f(z)
=\lim_{z\to i\frac{1}{r^{n}}}\frac{1}{r^n(r^nz+i)}\prod_{j=0,j\ne n}^\infty\frac{1}{(1+x^{2}r^{2j})}
=\large\frac{1}{2ir^n}\prod_{j=0,j\ne n}^\infty\frac{1}{(1-r^{2j-2n})}
